Package: Segvis
Type: Package
Title: Segviz: A package for visualization of high throughput sequencing data
    along genomic segments
Version: 0.00.2
Date: 2016-06-29
Author: Rene Welch <welch@stat.wisc.edu>
Maintainer: Rene Welch <welch@stat.wisc.edu>
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Rene", family = "Welch", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
     email = "[welch@stat.wisc.edu]")) 
Description: Calculates the coverage of a set of genomic regions
    given the fragments generated by sequencing experiments as ChIP-seq,
    ChIP-exo or ChIP-nexus.
